description:
&lt;p&gt;A vacancy for a full time Medical Secretary has arisen within the General Surgery department at the Queen Elizabeth the Queen Mother Hospital. This vacancy is to provide a comprehensive medical secretary/administrative service to consultants, clinicians and their teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Work in a team based secretarial service providing support for each other and ensuring continuity of the service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manage and monitor patients through their treatment pathway ensuring compliance to RTT and local waiting time standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Act as part of liaison between patients, GP’s, other staff and outside agencies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name:Jane Davis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title:Medical Secretary Supervisor&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address:jane.davis17@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 01843 235087&lt;/p&gt;
